hadiths[153]{hadithnumber,text}:
3089,"Hazrat Aamir Raami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham log apney ilaqey mein they ke hamarey liye jhandey aur nishaanaat buland kiye gaey ( hamarey ilaqey mein jihaadi muhimen pahunch gaeen). maine puchha ye kya hain? to logon ne kaha : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka jhandaa hai, chunanche main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap eik darkht ke nichey tashrif farma they, aap ke liye eik chadar bichhaai gaee thi aur aap us par baithey huey they aur aap ke Sahaba aap ke paas jama they. so mein bhi unke sath baith gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bimariyon ka zikr kiya, aapney farmaya : '' momin ko jab koi bimari aati hai aur phir Allah usey aafiyat aur shifa dey deta hai to wo uskey sabiqa gunahon ka kaffara bin jati hai aur aainda ke liye nasihat ka sabab hoti hai. aur munafiq jab bimar padta hai aur phir usey aafiyat di jati hai to uski misal oont ki si hoti hai jisey uskey ghar walon ne baandha ho aur phir khol diya ho. usey maloom nahin hota ke kyon baandha tha aur ye bhi maloom nahin hota ke kyon chhod diya hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke gird baithey huey logon mein se eik ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye bimariyaan kya hoti hain? main to Allah ki qasam ! kabhi bimar nahin hua . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uth ja , to ham mein se nahin hai.'' (phir kisi doosrey moqe par) ham aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they ke eik aadmi aaya, wo chadar odhey huey tha aur uskey haath mein kuchh tha jisey usney lapetaa hua tha. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab maine aap ko tashrif latey dekha to aap ki taraf chal pada . main darakhton ke eik jhund ke paas se guzra to us mein se parindey ke bachchon ki aawaz suni . isliye maine unhen pakad liya aur apni chadar mein dal liya . phir unki maa aai to merey sar par mandlaane lagi , maine uskey liye uskey bachchon ko nanga kiya to wo unke sath unke ooper aa padi , to maine inhen apni chadar mein lapet liya aur ye wohi merey paas hain. aapney farmaya : ''inhen chhod dey.'' to maine inhen chhod diya, magar unki maa ne ( ud janey sey) inkar kiya aur bachchon ke sath padi rahi. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba se farmaya : ''kya tum is maa ki apney bachchon par shafqat (meharbani) se tajjub kar rahey ho?'' unhoney kaha : haan , aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jisney mujhey haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai ! bila-shuba Allah taala apney bandon ke sath in bachchon ki maa se badh kar raheem aur shafiq hai. inhen wapis ley ja aur wahin rakh aa jahan se to ne inhen uthaya hai aur inki maa bhi sath rahey.'' chunanche wo aadmi inhen wapis ley gaya."
3090,"Muhammad bin Khalid se riwayat hai, Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Ibrahim bin Mehdi ne is raawi ( Muhammad bin Khalid (ke mutalliq kaha ke ye ''Sulmee'' hain wo apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, jinhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat ka sharf hasil tha, kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : ''beshak bandey ke liye jab Allah taala ke yahan koi maqam aur martaba muqaddar ho chuka ho aur wo apney aamaal ki bina par us tak na pahunch sakta ho, tu Allah usey uskey apney jism ya maal ya aulad ki aazmaesh mein dal deta hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne-Nufail ne ye izafa bayan kiya, , aur phir Allah taala usey sabr ki tofiq bhi deta hai.'' phir dono raawi hadees bayan karney mein muttafiq ho jatey hain.'' yahan tak ke usey us maqam aur martabe tak pahuncha deta hai jo Allah taala ki taraf se pehley hi se uskey liye muqaddar ho chuka hota hai.''"
3091,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se barhaa suna, aap farmatey they : ''jab koi banda nek amal karta raha ho magar bimari ya safar ki wajeh se wo na kar sakey tu Allah taala uskey liye wo amal usi tarah umda kaifiyat mein likhtaa rehta hai jabkey wo tandurust aur muqeem tha.''"
3092,"Hazrat Umme-Alaa' (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main bimar ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''aey Umme- Ala ! tumhen khushkhabri ho, bila-shuba musalman ki bimari ke zariey se Allah taala uskey gunahon ko khatam kar deta hai jaisey ke aag soney aur chaandi ka khot nikal deti hai.''"
3093,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo kehti hain : maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main khoob jaanti hun ke Quran majeed mein sab se sakht aayat kon si hai. aapney farmaya : '' kon si aayat hai wo? aey Aaisha !'' kehti hain, maine kaha : Allah taala ka ye farman : (من يعمل سوءا يجز به) ''jisney bhi koi burai ki, usey uska badla diya jaeyga.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! kya tumhen maloom nahin ke momin ko jo koi pareshani aati hai ya kaanta bhi chubh jata hai to usey uskey kisi sab se burey amal ka badla dey diya jata hai aur jis ka hisab liya gaya to usey azab hua.'' kehti hain ke maine arz kiya : to kya Allah ne nahin farmaya : ( فسوف يحاسب حسابا يسيرا ) ''an-qareeb bandey ka hisab liya jaeyga aasan hisab?'' Aapney farmaya : ''us se murad Allah taala ke samney haziri hai, aey Aaisha ! jis se hisab mein poochh gachh ho gaee , usey azab hua. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye ibne Bashaar ke lafz hain. aur iski sanad mein (عن(an)) ki bajaey ( (اخبرنا ابن أبي مليكة) hai."
3094,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abdullah bin Ubai (munafiq) ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey, us bimari mein jis mein ke wo mar gaya tha. chunanche jab aap uskey yahaan pahunchey to aapney us par maut ke asraat mehsoos kiye (aur) farmaya : ''main tujhey mana kya karta tha ke yahood se mohabbat na rakh.'' usney kaha : Asaad bin Zarara ne un se bughz rakha to kya hua? phir jab wo mar gaya to uska beta ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! beshak Abdullah bin Ubai mar gaya hai, to aap mujhey apni qamis inayat farma den ke main usey is mein kafan dun to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni qamis utaar kar usey dey di."
3095,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke yahudiyon ka eik ladka bimar ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey . aap uskey sar ke paas baith gaey, aur us se farmaya : ''Islam qubul kar lo.'' to usney apney baap ki taraf dekha jabke wo bhi uskey sar ke paas hi baitha hua tha. to uskey baap ne us se kaha : Abul-Qaasim ki baat maan lo. chunanche usney Islam qubul kar liya. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se uthey to farma rahey they : ''hamd us Allah ki jisney isko merey zariey se aag se najat di.''"
3096,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif latey , baghair iskey ke kisi khachchar par Sawar hon ya ghodey par."
3097,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney wuzu kiya aur achchha wuzu kiya aur sawab ki niyat se apney musalman bhai ki iyaadat ke liye gaya to usey jahannam se sattar saal ki masafat (doori) par door kar diya jaeyga.'' Sabit Bunani kehtey hain maine puchha : aey Abu-Hamza ! ( [ خريف ] ( se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : saal. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ehle-Basra jin ahadis ke bayan kerney mein munfarid hain un mein se eik ye bhi hai ke insan baa-wuzoo ho kar iyaadat ke liye jaey."
3098,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jo shakhs shaam ke waqt kisi mareez ki iyaadat ke liye nikalta hai to uskey sath sattar hazar farishtey bhi nikaltey hain jo uskey liye subah tak bakhshish talab kartey rehtey hain aur jannat mein usey eik baagh bhi hasil hoga , aur jo koi subah ke waqt iyaadat ke liye nikley to uskey sath sattar hazar farishtey nikaltey hain jo uskey liye shaam tak bakhshish maangtey rehtey hain aur jannat mein usey eik baagh bhi hasil hoga."
3099,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya, lekin us mein) [ خريف ] ( yani baagh ka zikr nahin hai. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : is hadees ko Mansoor ne bhi hukm se aisey hi riwayat kya hai jaisey ke Shoba ne ."
3100,"abu-Jaafar Abdullah bin Naafe se riwayat hai, . . aur Naafe Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke ghulam they. . . . bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur phir hadees Shoba ke ham-maani bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko b-waasta Hazrat Ali , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaee eik sahih sanadon se riwayat kya gaya hai."
3101,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Hazrat Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) jang khandaq mein zakhmi ho gaey . eik aadmi ne unke bazu ki rag (rag haft andaam) par nishana maara tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye masjid mein khema lagwa liya taake qarib se unki iyaadat kartey rahen .
3102,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kehtey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye jabkey meri aankh mein dard tha."
3103,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, wo kehtey hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab tum suno ke falan ilaqey mein taaoon phel gaya hai to phir wahan mat jao, aur jab kahen phel jaey aur tum wahan ho to us ( taaoon ( se farar ikhtiyar kartey huey wahan se mat niklo.''"
3104,"Hazrat Aaisha, Saad abi Waqas (Raziallahu anha) ki beti se marwi (bayan) hai ke unke walid ne bayan kya ke main Makka mein bimar ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar pursi ke liye merey yahan tashrif laye, aapney apna haath Mubarak meri peshani par rakha, phir merey seeney aur pet par phera aur farmaya : ''aey Allah! Saad ko shifa inayat farma aur uski hijrat mukammal farma dey.''"
3105,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bhookey ko khana khilao , mareez ki bimar pursi karo aur qaidi ko chhudaao. Sufiyan ne wazahat ki ke) [ العاني ] ( se murad qaidi hai."
3106,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi aisey mareez ki iyaadat ki jiski abhi ajal na aai ho, to saat baar uskey paas ye dua : [أسأل الله العظيم ، رب العرش العظيم ، أن يشفيك] ''main Allah se sawal karta hun jo azmat aur badai wala aur arshe-azeem ka rab hai ke tujhey shifa inayat farmaey.'' padhey, tu Allah taala usey us bimari se aafiyat dey dega.''"
3107,"Hazrat ( Abdullah (bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi shakhs kisi mareez ki iyaadat ke liye jaey, to chahiye ke yun kahiye [اللهم اشف عبدك ، ينكأ لك عدوا ، أو يمشي لك إلى جنازة] ''aey Allah ! apney bandey ko shifa inayat farma , ye teri raah mein kisi dushman ko zakhmi kerega ya teri raza ke liye kisi janaza mein shareek hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne-Sarah (Ahmed bin Amr bin Abdullah) ne ( [ إلى janaaza ] ( ki bajaey ( [ إلى صلاة ] ( riwayat kya hai. yani ye banda Namaz ke liye jaeyga ."
3108,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi dukh ke aaney par koi shakhs hergiz maut ki dua na karey, balke chahiye ke yun kahey ( [ اللهم أحيني ما كانت الحياة خيرا لي , وتوفني إذا كانت الوفاة خيرا لي ] ( ''aey Allah ! mujhey zinda rakh jab tak ke zindagi merey liye khair ka baais ho aur jab maut merey liye behtar ho to mujhey wafat dey dey .''"
3109,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs hergiz hergiz maut ki tamanna na karey.'' aur mazkura baala riwayat ke misl bayan kya."
3110,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Khalid Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, . . jo ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se they. . . . unhon (Musaddad) ne eik baar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aur eik baar Ubaid se riwayat kya : ''achanak maut narazi ki pakad hai.''"
3111,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abdullah bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye to usey be hosh paya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey zara zor se bulaya, magar usney jawab na diya, to aapney إنا لله وإنا إليه راجعون padha aur farmaya : ''aey abu Rabee! terey maamley mein ham maghloob hain ( Allah ka faisla aur uski taqdir hi ghalib hai.'' ( to aurten cheekh padin aur roney lagen . ibn Ateek unhen khamosh karaney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen chhod do magar jab maamla Sabit ho jaey to phir koi hergiz na roey .'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( وجوب ( ) maamla Sabit ho janey ( se kya murad hai? aapney farmaya : '' maut .'' uski eik beti ( Abdullah ke mutalliq ( kehney lagi : mujhey to umeed thi ke Allah taala tumhen shahadat se sarfaraaz farmaeyga aur aapney apna saman jihad bhi tayyar kar liya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah azz-w-jall ne uska ajr uski niyat ke mutabiq dey diya hai. aur tum log shahadat kisey samajhtey ho?'' wo kehney lagey ke Allah ki raah mein qatl ho jana . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein qatl ke ilawa bhi shahadat ke saat asbab hain : taaoon se marney wala Shahid hai, pani mein doob janey wala Shahid hai, zaatul-janb se mar janey wala Shahid hai (zaatul-janb eik sakht qism ki bimari hai jis mein pasli ke andar eik phoda ho jata hai aksar taur par aadmi us se halak ho jata.), pet ki takleef se mar janey wala Shahid hai, aag mein jal marney wala Shahid hai, kisi makaan ya deewar ke nichey aa kar mar janey wala Shahid hai aur wo aurat, jo wiladat ki takleef (drde-zeh) mein wafat pa jaey, Shahid hai. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : ( [ الجمع ] ( se murad ye hai ke bacha bhi aurat ke sath ho ( mar jaey .)"
3112,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : bano Haris bin Aamir bin Nofal ne Hazrat khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko kharida liya , aur khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) hi wo shakhs they jinhon ne Badr ki ladai mein Haris bin Aamir ka kaam tamam kya tha. chunanche khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan qaidi rahey yahan tak ke un logon ne unko Shahid kerney ka faisla kar liya , chunanche ( qatl kiye janey se kuch din pehley ( unhoney Haris ki beti se ustara talab kya taake zere-naaf ki safai kar lein , to wo usney unko dey diya. phir uska eik chhota bacha ghisat-tey ghisat-tey unke paas aa gaya jabkey wo us se ghafil thi , to jab usney achcha dekha ke bacha akela hi khubaib ke paas , uski raan par betha hai aur ustara bhi unke haath mein hai to wo ye manzar dekh kar dehshat zada ho gaee jisey khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhaanp liya , to wo boley : kya tum darti ho ke main usey qatl kar dalunga, nahin, nahin main ye kaam nahin karunga . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Shuaib bin abi Hamza ne ye qissa Zohri ke wastey riwayat kya, to kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah bin Ayaz ne bayan kya ke Haris ki beti ne usey bataya ke un logon ne jab ye faisla kya ke wo khubeb (Raziallahu anhu) ko qatl kar dalengey to unhoney us ladki se ustara talab kya taake zere-naaf ki safai kar lein to wo usney unhen dey diya."
3113,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aapney apni wafat se teen roz pehley farmaya tha : ''tum mein se kisi ki maut na aaye magar us haal mein ke wo Allah ke sath umda guman rakhta ho.''"
3114,Hazrat abu-Salma bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ka waqt qarib aaya to unhoney naey kapdey mangwaaey aur pehan liye . phir kehney lagey : beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha ke '' maiyat ko unhi kapdon mein uthaya jaeyga jin mein usey maut aaeygi .''
3115,"Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum kisi qaribul-maut aadmi ke paas jao to achi baat bolo. bila-shuba tum jo kuch boltey ho us par farishtey aameen kehtey hain.'' jab Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main kya kahun? aapney farmaya : tum yun kaho : ( [ اللهم اغفر له , وأعقبنا عقبى صالحة ] ( ''aey Allah ! uski bakhshish farma . aur hamen uskey baad behtareen saleh badal inayat farma.'' kehti hain : phir Allah taala ne mujhey us ( abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu)) ke badley mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) inayat farma diye."
3116,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiski aakhiri baat ( [ La-ilaah-illallah ] ( '' ho wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.''"
3117,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney marney walon ko kalma ( [ La-ilaah-illallah ] ( ki talqin karo.''"
3118,"Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye jabkey ( rooh qabz honey ke baad) unki nazar phat gaee thi , to aapney unki aankhen band kar din. ab unke ghar waley cheekh w pukar kerney lagey , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney liye bad duayen mat karo, balke achey bol bolo , kyonkey jo tum kehtey ho us par farishtey aameen kehtey hain.'' phir aapney ( bator dua ( farmaya : ''aey Allah ! abu-Salma ki bakhshish farma , hidayat yafta logon ke sath uskey darjaat buland kar aur uskey peechey reh janey walon mein to hi uska Khalifa ban. aur aey rabbul-aalameen! hamari aur uski maghfirat farma , aey Allah ! uski qabr ko faraakh aur roshan kar dey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maiyat ki aankhen uski rooh nikal janey ke baad band ki jaeyn . kehtey hain : maine Muhammad bin Muhammad bin Noman al-muqri se suna, wo kehtey they maine abu-Maisra se suna jo ke eik abid insan they, wo kehtey they maine Jaafar al-muallim ki haalat maut ( نزع ( mein aankhen band kar din . . . . aur ye eik abid insan they. . . . to maine usi raat khuwab mein dekha ke wo mujh se keh rahey they : meri maut se pehley hi tumhara meri aankhen band kar dena merey liye bahut badi baat thi."
3119,"ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko koi musibat aa padey, to chahiye ke yun kahey(إنا لله وإنا إليه راجعون ، اللهم ! عندك أحتسب مصيبتي ، فآجرني فيها ، وأبدل لي خيرا منها)''ham Allah ke liye hain aur usi ki taraf lot janey waley hain. aey Allah ! is musibat mein, main tujh se ajr w sawab ki umeed rakhta hun, mujhey is mein ajr inayat farma aur us (mafqood) ke badley mujhey us se badh kar behtar badal inayat farma.''"
3120,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko) unki wafat par) eik naqsh hui dhaaridaar chadar se dhanp di gaee thi.
3121,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney marney walon par sura Yaseen padha karo.'' aur ye lafz ibne-al-Ula ke hain."
3122,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo bayan karti hain ke jab hazraat Zaid bin Harisa , Jaafar bin Abi Talib aur Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ki shahaadatein huin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein baith gaey. aap ke chehrey par gham ke asraat numaya they. aur (raawi ne) qissa bayan kiya."
3123,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main eik maiyat ko dafn kiya. jab ham farigh huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis lautey, ham bhi aap ke sath wapis huey. jab aap apney darwazey ke samney aaye to ruk gaey, ham ne dekha ke eik khatoon aa rahi hai, mera khayal hai ke aapney usey pehchan liya tha. jab wo janey lagi to maloom hua ke wo Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) thin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Fatima ! tum apney ghar se kyon nikli ho?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main un ghar walon ke paas aai thi aur maine unki maiyat ke liye dua aur uskey mutalliq ta'ziyat ki hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur to shayad unke sath kuda (qabron ki taraf ( bhi gaee hogi ?'' unhoney kaha : Allah ki panah ! jabke maine aap ko is baarey mein farmatey suna hai jo aap farmatey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to unke sath kuda jati to . . . .'' aapney badi sakht baat zikr farmaee. (Mufazzal kehtey hain ke) maine Rabeea se kuda ke baarey mein maloom kiya to unhoney kaha : main samajhta hun ke us jagah qabren hain."
3124,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aurat ke paas se guzrey jo apney bachchey par ro rahi thi aapney us se farmaya : ''Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar kar aur sabr kar.'' wo boli tumhen meri musibat ki kya parwa? us aurat se kaha gaya : ye to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. tab wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir hui , usney aap ke darwazey par chaukeedaar na paey . usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine aap ko pehchaana nahin tha, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sabr wohi hota hai jo pehley sadme ke waqt ho.''"
3125,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik sahibzadi ne aap ko paigham bheja , jabkey main , Saad bin Ubada aur ghaaliban Abi (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they, mera beta ya beti naz'aa ki keyfiyat mein hai to aap tashrif ley aaeyn . aapney jawab mein salam kahlwaayaa aur farmaya : ''usey kaho ke Allah jo le-ley aur jo inayat farma dey sab usi ka hai aur har chiz ka uskey yahaan eik waqt muqarrar hai.'' usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dobara qasam de-kar bulwaya to aap tashrif ley gaey . phir bachchey ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki god mein dey diya gaya jabke wo dam tod raha tha. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aankhen beh padin . Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye kya? aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba ye rehmat hai, Allah jinkey mutalliq chahta hai unke dilon mein usey dal deta hai aur Allah apney unhi bandon par rehmat farmata hai jo rehem dil hon.''"
3126,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khabar di : ''merey yahan aaj raat eik bachcha paida hua hai. maine uska naam apney walid ke naam par ''Ibrahim'' rakha hai.'' aur hadees bayan ki . Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : maine usey dekha ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haathon mein (aalame naz'aa mein)(jaan nikalne ke qareeb) be chain ho raha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aankhen beh padin , phir aapney farmaya : '' aankh roti hai, dil intehai ghamgin hai aur ham wohi kehtey hain jis mein hamarey Rab ki raza hai. Ibrahim ! terey firaaq par ham ghamgin hain.''"
3127,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhoney kaha : be-shak , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein nauha karney se mana farmaya hai."
3128,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nauha kerney wali aur usey sunney wali par lanat farmaee hai."
3129,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba maiyat ko uskey ghar walon ke roney ki wajeh se azab hota hai.'' ye hadees Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke samney bayan ki gaee , to unhoney kaha : ( Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bhool gaey hain, haqeeqat ye hai ke) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik qabr ke paas se guzrey they, to farmaya tha : ''beshak ye qabr wala azab diya ja raha hai aur uskey ghar waley is par ro rahey hain.'' phir Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne ye aayat padhi : (ولا تزر وازرة وزر أخرى) ''koi jaan kisi dusri jaan ka bojh nahin uthaey gi.'' Hannaad ne Abu-Muaawia se riwayat kartey huey wazahat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik yahudi ki qabr ke paas se guzrey they."
3130,"Hazrat Yazid bin Aus kehtey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya jabke wo ( bimari ke baais ( bahut hi takleef mein they, to unki biwi roney lagi ya uski tayyari kerney lagi. Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : kya to ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman nahin suna? kehney lagi : haan , maine suna hai. chunanche wo khamosh ho rahi. jab Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ho gaee to Yazid kehtey hain ke main us khatoon se mila aur us se puchha ke wo kya baat thi jo Abu-Musa ne aap se kahi thi ke kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman nahin suna aur phir aap khamosh ho rahi thin? unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''jo koi (musibat mein) baal moondey ya bayan karey (ya munh peetey) ya kapdey phaadey wo ham mein se nahin hai.''"
3131,"Hazrat Usaid bin Abi Usaid eik khatoon se bayan kartey hain jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baiat ki thi , kehti hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se jo ehad liye they ke neki ke kamon mein ham aap ki nafarmani nahin kerengi . . . . us mein ye bhi tha ke chehra nahin nochengi, haaye-waaye nahin kerengi , kapdey nahin phaadengi gi aur baal nahin nochengi."
3132,Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya tha : ''aale Jaafar ke liye khana tayyar karo bila-shuba unhen eik aisa maamla darpesh hai jisney unhen mashghool kar diya hai.'' (unke paas Hazrat Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ki khabar aai thi.)
3133,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : eik shakhs ko uskey seeney ya halaq main eik teer aa laga aur wo faut ho gaya to usey usi tarah uskey kapdon mein lapet diya gaya. kehtey hain : (us waqia mein) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they."
3134,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shohdaaey uhud ke mutalliq farmaya tha : ''unke hathiyar aur) chamdey ki) posteen utaar liye jaeyn aur unhen unke khoonon aur kapdon hi mein dafn kiya jaey. [ye alfaz Ziyad bin Ayub ke hain].
3135,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke shohdaaey uhud ko ghusl nahin diya gaya , unhen unke khoonon ke sath hi dafn kar diya gaya aur janaza bhi nahin padha gaya."
3136,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey jabke unka musla kiya gaya tha. (unki laash se naak aur kaan waghaira kaat liye gaey they.) to aapney farmaya : ''agar ye baat na ho ke (unki behan) Safiya ((Raziallahu anha) ( se bardasht nahin ho sakega to main usey ( Hazrat Hamza ki lasah ko) aisey hi chhod dun yahan tak ke usey darindey aur parindey kha jaeyn aur phir ye unke peton hi se mehshar mein ayen.'' aur (uhud mein) kapdey kam pad gaey aur maqtooleen ki tadaad bahut ziyada ho gaee to eik eik do do aur teen teen ko eik hi kapdey mein kafan diya gaya. Quteba ne mazeed kaha : aur eik eik qabr mein dafn kiye gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke mutalliq daryaft farmatey jatey they ke in mein se Quran kis ko ziyada yaad hai? phir usey qible ki janib aagey kar detey they.
3137,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey (aur dekha ke) unka musla kiya gaya hai to aapney unke siwa kisi aur ka janaza nahin padha.
3138,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shohdaaey uhud mein se do do aadmiyon ko ikhatta kartey aur daryaft farmatey : ''in mein Quran kisey ziyada yaad hai?'' jab kisi eik ki taraf ishara kiya jata , to aap usey lahad mein aagey rakhtay. aur aapney farmaya : ''main qiyamat ke roz inke liye gawah hounga.'' aapney hukm diya ke inhen inke khoonon hi mein dafn kiya jaey aur inhen ghusl nahin diya."
3139,Hazrat Leis ne is hadees ko mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya aur kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shohdaaey uhud mein se do do aadmiyon ko eik eik kafan mein ikhatta kiya.
3140,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni raan (jaangh) uriyaan (nangi) na kar aur na kabhi kisi zinda ya maiyat ki raan ko dekh.''"
3141,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Sahaba kiram ne jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghusl dena chaha to unhoney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! hamein maloom nahin ke aaya ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kapdey utaaren jaisey ke ham apni maiyaton ke utaar detey hain ya unhen unke kapdon samet hi ghusl den. isliye jab unka is baarey mein ikhtilaf hua , tu Allah ne un par neend taari kar di , un mein se koi bhi na bacha magar uski thodi uskey seeney se ja lagi . phir ghar ki janib se eik baat karney waley ne baat ki, kisi ko khabar nahin ke wo kon tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko unke kapdon samet hi ghusl do . chunanche wo uthey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aap ki qamis samet ghusl diya. wo qamis ke ooper hi se pani daltey jatey they aur aap ki qamis hi se aap ko maltey jatey they baghair iskey ke aap ke jism ko unke haath lagen. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kaha karti thin : agar mujhey is maamley ka pehley ilm ho jata jis ka baad mein hua hai, to aap ko aap ki azwaaj (biwiyan) hi ghusl detin."
3142,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye jabkey aap ki sahibzadi ki wafat ho gaee thi. aapney farmaya : ''usey teen ya paanch baar ghusl do ya us se bhi ziyada agar zarurat mehsoos karo, aisey pani ke sath jis mein beri ke pattey miley hon, aur aakhiri baar mein kuchh kaafur bhi mila lena , aur jab tum ghusl se farigh ho jao to mujhey khabar dena.'' chunanche jab ham farigh ho gaey to aap ko khabar di to aapney hamein apna tehband diya aur farmaya : ''isey uskey jism ke sath lapet do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) se ( [ حقو ] ( ki bajaey ( [ إزار ]) ka lafz marwi (bayan) hai. (aur maani eik hi hai yani tehband (aur Musaddad ne ( [ دخل علينا] (ke alfaz bayan nahin kiye."
3143,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham ne ( dukhtare-Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tajheez aur takfeen mein) unke baalon ki teen laten banai thin.
3144,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham ne unke baalon ki teen laten baat din aur phir un laton ko in (mohtarma) ke peechhey dal diya, yani sar ke aagey ke baal aur dono atraaf (aas-paas)waley."
3145,Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen apni sahibzadi ke ghusl ke baarey mein farmaya tha : ''unki daain traf aur wuzu ke angon se ghusl shuru keren.''
3146,"Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahimahullah) ne Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se hadees bayan ki jo Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ki riwayat ke ham-maani hai. aur hadees Hafsa ( binte Sirin ( jo Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai is mein bhi usi ki manind hai, lekin is mein ye izafa hai : ''ya saat baar ghusl do ya is se ziyada agar zarurat mehsoos karo.''"
3147,Janab Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahimahullah) ghusl maiyat ki riwayat Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kya kartey they. (ye ghusle-maiyat ka tariqa unhoney umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) se seekha tha (aur wo maiyat ko do baar beri ke pani se nahlaatey aur teesri baar kaafur miley pani se.
3148,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz khutba irshad farmaya aur is mein apney eik sahabi ka zikr kiya jo faut ho gaya tha aur usko maamuli kafan diya gaya aur raat hi mein dafn kar diya gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is baat par daantaa ke raat ke waqt kisi ko dafn na kiya jaey yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uska janaza padh lein siwaey iske ke koi majboori ho. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney bhai ko kafan dey to umda kafan dey.''
3149,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (pehley) (chhapi dhaari daar chadar ka ( kafan pehnaya gaya tha magar usey utaar liya gaya.
3150,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' ham mein se jab koi faut ho jaey aur usey wusat hasil ho, to chahiye ke uska kafan munaqqash dhaari daar chadar ka ho.''"
3151,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen safed yamni kapdon mein kafan diya gaya tha, un mein qamis thi, na pagdi."
3152,"Hisham bin Urwa ne b-waasta apney walid , Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se uskey misl riwayat kya aur mazeed kaha ke ye kapdey suti they. unhoney bayan kya ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se logon ki ye baat zikr ki gaee ke '' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko do kapdon aur eik munaqqash dhaari daar chadar mein kafan diya gaya tha.'' to unhoney kaha : mukhattat chadar laee gaee thi magar unhoney usey wapis kar diya tha aur us mein kafan nahin diya tha."
3153,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen najraani kapdon mein kafan diya gaya. eik hulla jo do kapdon par mushtamil tha aur eik unki apni qamis jis mein unki wafat hui. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Usman bin abi Sheba ne kaha : teen kapdon mein kafan diya gaya. eik surkh hulla aur eik qamis , jis mein aap ki wafat hui ."
3154,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke kafan mahnga nahin hona chahiye. beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' kafan mahngaa mat banaya karo, bila-shuba ye bahut jald chheen liya jata hai.''"
3155,"Hazrat Khabbab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Musab bin Umair (Raziallahu anhu) Uhud ke roz Shahid ho gaey. unke paas eik hi safed w siyah dhaari daar ooni chadar thi. ham jab us se unka sar dhaanptey to unke paon nikal aatey aur jab paon dhaanptey to unka sar nanga ho jata , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se unka sar dhanp do aur qadmon par thodi si izkhir (ghaas) dal do.''"
3156,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwaayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' behtareen kafan hulla hai) do chadaren (aur behtarin qurbani mendha hai jo seengon wala ho.''"
3157,"Hazrat Leila bint Qanif Saqifa bayan karti hain ke main un aurton mein shamil thi jinhon ne Hazrat Umme- kulsoom Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti ko unki wafat ke waqt ghusl diya tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen ( unke kafan ke liye ( sab se pehley apna tehband inayat farmaya , phir qamis , phir odhni, phir eik chadar unko lapetney ke liye , phir un ( kapdon (ke baad unko eik doosrey kapdey mein lapeta gaya. bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kafan liye darwazey ke paas tashrif farma they aur hamen eik eik kapda detey jatey they."
3158,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhari khushbuon mein se behtareen khushbu kastoori hai.''"
3159,"Husain bin Wahuh se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Talha bin Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bimar ho gaey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''mera khayal hai ke Talha ki maut aa gaee hai. (jab unki wafat ho jaey) to mujhey ittilaa dena aur jaldi karna , munasib nahin ke musalman ki maiyat uskey ghar walon ke paas padi rahey .''"
3160,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaar baaton se ghusl kya kartey they : (1) janabat se (2) Juma ke roz (3) singi lagwa kar (4) aur maiyat ko ghusl de-kar .
3161,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi maiyat ko nehlaaey wo ghusl karey aur jo usey uthaey wo wuzu karey.''"
3162,"Is-haq maula Zayda ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uskey ham-maani riwayat kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hukm mansookh hai, maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, un se sawal kya gaya ke maiyat ko nehlaney se ghusl karna kaisey hai? unhoney kaha uskey liye wuzu kafi hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : abu-Saaleh ne is hadees ki sanad mein apney aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmiyan '' Is-haq maula Zayda ''ko badha diya hai. aur mazkura baala hadees Musab bin Sheba (hadees : 3160 ( zaeef hai. us mein kaee baaten hain jin par amal nahin."
3163,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aapney Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ko bosa diya jabkey wo faut ho gaey they, maine dekha ke aap ke aansu beh rahey they."
3164,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke (eik baar) logon ne qabristaan mein roshni dekhi, wahan gaey to dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabr mein utrey huey hain aur farma rahey hain : ''apna sahab mujhey pakdaao.'' phir maloom hua ke ye wo aadmi tha jo Allah ke zikr ( tilawat Quran (ke sath apni aawaz buland kya karta tha."
3165,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke ham Uhud ke shahidon ko dafn kerney ke liye utha laye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka manadi aaya aur kaha : beshak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen hukm detey hain ke un maqtulon ko unke maqamate-shahadat hi par dafn karo, chunanche ham ne unhen wahin lota diya."
3166,"Hazrat Malik bin Hubera (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi musalman faut ho jaey aur phir us par musalmanon ki teen safein janaza padhein tu Allah uskey liye ( jannat ( lazim kar deta hai.'' bayan kya ke Hazrat Malik (Raziallahu anhu) jab kisi janaze mein logon ki tadaad kam paatey to unhen teen safon mein taqseem kar diya kartey they."
3167,Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham aurton ko janaazey ke sath janey se mana kya gaya hai magar ham par sakhti nahin ki gaee.
3168,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke jo shakhs janaazey ke sath gaya aur phir us par Namaz padhi to uskey liye eik qeeraat ajr hai, aur jo uskey sath gaya yahan tak ke (dafn sey) faraaghat ho gaee to uskey liye do qeeraat hain. un dono qeeraaton mein se chhota Uhud pahad ke barabar hoga ya farmaya ke un main eik qeeraat ahad pahad jitna hoga."
3169,"Janab Dawud bin Aamir bin Saad bin abi Waqas , apney walid ( Aamir ( se bayan kartey hain ke wo ( Aamir ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas they ke Janab Khabbab sahab maqsoora tashrif laye aur kaha : aey Abdullah bin umr ! kya aapney suna ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kya kehtey hain? unka kehna hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''jo shakhs janaazey waley ghar se uskey sath nikla aur us par Namaz padhi . . . .'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne ye hadees Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchhwai to unhoney farmaya : Abu-Huraira ne sach kaha hai."
3170,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''jo koi musalman faut ho jaey aur phir us par chaalis aadmi khadey ho kar janaza padhein , jo Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek na thehratey hun, to us maiyat ke baarey mein unki sifarish qubul kar li jati hai.''"
3171,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' janaazey ke sath koi aawaz ya aag na jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud ne farmaya : (raawi hadees) Harun ne ye izafa bayan kya hai : '' aag uskey aagey aagey na ley jaai jaey.''"
3172,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea se riwayat hai, unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees pahunchi : ''jab tum janaza dekho to uskey liye khadey ho jao yahan tak ke aagey guzar jaey ya usey nichey rakh diya jaey.''"
3173,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum janazey ke sath jao to jab tak usey nichey na rakh diya jaey, mat betho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko) Sufiyan ( Sauri ne b-waasta Suhel , uskey walid se aur usney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. aur us mein kaha : '' yahan tak ke usey zameen par rakh diya jaey.'' jabkey abu-Muaawia ne Suhel se riwayat kartey huey kaha : '' yahan tak ke usey lehad mein rakh diya jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Sufiyan ( Sauri ( abu-Muaawia ki nisbat ziyada haafiz they."
3174,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they ke hamarey paas se eik janaza guzra, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey liye khadey ho gaey . jab ham ne usko kandha dena chaha to maloom hua ke ye yahudi ka janaza hai. ham ne arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye yahudi ka janaza hai. aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba maut eik dardnak hadisa hai, jab tum koi janaza dekho to uskey liye khadey ho jaya karo.''"
3175,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) janaazon ko dekh kar khadey ho jaya kartey they, magar baad mein bethney lag gaey they."
3176,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) janaazey ke liye khadey rehtey they yahan tak ke usey lahad mein utaar diya jata , eik yahudi aalim ka aap ke paas se guzar hua to usney kaha : ham bhi aisey hi kartey hain. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey aur farmaya : ''beth jao. unki mukhalifat karo.''"
3177,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik janaze ke sath they, to aap ko sawari pesh ki gaee magar aapney Sawar honey se inkar kar diya, phir jab wapis huey aur sawari pesh ki gaee to aap Sawar ho gaey . us baarey mein aap se puchha gaya to farmaya : ''tehqiq farishtey chal rahey they to mujhey laaiq na tha ke wo chal rahey hon aur main Sawar ho jaun , jab wo chaley gaey to main Sawar ho gaya .''"
3178,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat ibn Dahdah (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza padhaya aur ham us mein mojud they, phir eik ghoda la kar baandh diya gaya yahan tak ke aap us par Sawar ho gaey, phir wo aap ke sath darmiyani raftaar se tez tez chalney laga aur ham bhi aap ke sath ird-gird mein tez tez chalney lagey ."
3179,"Hazrat Salim apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha ke ye log janaza ke aagey aagey chaltey they."
3180,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' Sawar aadmi janaza ke peechey chaley aur pedal log uskey peechey, aagey, daain aur baaeyn uskey qarib qarib chalen, aur bacha jo naqis paida ho uski bhi Namaz janaza padhi jaey aur uskey maa baap ke liye maghfirat aur rehmat ki dua ki jaey.''"
3181,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : '' janaza jaldi ley jao, agar wo nek aur saleh hai to tum usey bhalai ki taraf aagey ley ja rahey ho aur agar wo uskey siwa hai to wo eik shar hai jisey tum apni gardanon se utaar phenk rahey ho.''"
3182,"Hazrat Uena bin Abdur-Rehman apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke janaazey mein shareek they aur ham maiyat ko uthaey aahista aahista chal rahey they, Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) hamen peechey se aan miley to unhoney apna koda buland kya aur kaha : main dekh raha hun ke goya ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hotey they aur) maiyat ko utha kar) darmiyani chaal se dod rahey hotey they."
3183,Khalid bin Haris aur Esa bin Yunus ne Uena bin Abdur-Rehman se ye riwayat naqal ki to un dono ne Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) ke janaazey ka zikr kya. aur kaha ke (abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu)) apna khachar doda kar laye aur apney kodey se ishara kya.
3184,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke janaazey ke sath chalney ka kya adab hai? to aapney farmaya : '' darmiyani si tez raftaar se chala jaey, agar wo nek hai to bhalai ki taraf jaldi ley jatey ho aur agar wo uskey siwa hai to dozakhiyon ke liye halakat hai. janaza aagey aagey hona chahiye, peechey nahin hona chahiye aisa na ho ke koi uskey aagey chaley . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat zaeef hai) Yahya Mujbir ( ye Yahya bin Abdullah hai aur yehi Yahya Jabir hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye kufi hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Abu-Majida Basri, ghair maroof raawi hai."
3185,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs bimar ho gaya, (uskey ghar waley) us par roney lagey. to uska hamsaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kehney laga ke wo aadmi faut ho gaya hai. aapney farmaya : '' tujhey kya khabar?'' usney kaha : maine usey dekha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba wo nahin mara hai.'' to wo lot gaya. ghar waley us aadmi par phir roney lagey to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke wo mar gaya hai. Nabi karim ne farmaya : '' wo nahin mara hai, to wo lot gaya. to log us par phir roney lagey . uski biwi ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jao aur unhein khabar karo . us aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ! is par lanat kar . phir wo aadmi aaya aur dekha ke usney apney aap ko teer (ya neze (ke phal se jo uskey paas tha zibeh kar liya tha. to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf chala aur aap ko khabar di ke wo mar gaya hai. aapney kaha : ''tumhen kaisey khabar hui?'' usney kaha : maine usey dekha hai ke usney neze ke phal ke sath apney aap ko zabah kar liya hai. aapney puchha : ''kya to ne khud usey dekha hai? '' usney kaha : haan . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tab main uski Namaz janaza nahin padhunga.''"
3186,Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) par Namaze-janaza nahin padhi lekin doosron ko roka nahin tha.
3187,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo bayan karti hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farzand arjumand Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ho gaee jabkey unki umr 18 maah thi , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska janaza nahin padha tha."
3188,"Wayel bin Dawud ne kaha ke maine Bahi se suna, wo kehtey they : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farzand Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqam maqaaid mein unki Namaz janaza padhi thi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : maine Saeed bin Yaqoob taaliqani par qirat ki, un se puchha gaya ke kya aap ko ibne-mubarak an (an) Yaqoob bin Qaaqaa b-waasta Ata Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees pahunchi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney sahibzadey Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza padha tha jabkey wo sattar dino ka tha."
3189,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, wo kehti hain : qasam Allah ki ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baiza ke bete Suhel ki Namaz janaza masjid hi mein padhi thi."
3190,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah ki qasam ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baiza ke do beton Suhel aur uskey bhai ki Namaz janaza masjid mein ada farmaai thi.
3191,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi maiyat ka janaza masjid mein ada kya to us par koi gunah nahin.''"
3192,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke teen oqaat ke mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen mana farmaya kartey they ke ham un mein Namaz padhein ya apni maiyaton ko dafn keren : jab Suraj nikal raha ho yahan tak ke buland ho jaey, aen do-pehar ( zawal (ke waqt yahan tak ke dhal jaey aur jab ghuroob honey ke qarib ho yahan tak ke ghuroob ho jaey. raawi kehta hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke alfaz isi ke qarib they."
3193,"Hazrat Ammar maula Haris bin Nofal bayan kartey hain ke wo Umme- kulsoom (dukhtar Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) zauja mohtarma Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) (aur unke sahibzadey ( Zaid akbar (ke janaazey mein hazir they. pas ( ameer Madina ne ( bachey ko Imam ki taraf rakha to maine uska inkar kya, jamaat mein hazraat ibne-Abbas, abu-Saeed Khudri , abu-Qatada aur Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) mojud they, to unhoney kaha : yehi sunnat hai."
3194,"Hazrat Naafe Abu Ghalib (Rahimahullah) ka bayan hai ke main (Basra mein) marbad mohalle ki eik gali mein tha ke eik janaza guzra, uskey sath bahut se log they. logon ne kaha : ye Abdullah bin Umair ka janaza hai to main bhi uskey sath ho liya . maine eik aadmi dekha jo eik bareek si ooni chadar odhey huey apney chhotey se ghodey par Sawar tha, dhoop se bachao ke liye usney apney sar par kapda rakha hua tha. maine puchha : ye mohtaram buzurg kon hain? logon ne kaha : ye (Sahibe-Rasool) Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) hain. chunanche jab maiyat ko rakha gaya to Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur uska janaza padhaya, mein unke peechhey tha merey aur unke darmiyan koi chiz haael (rukawat) na thi. aap is maiyat ke sar ke muqabil khadey huey aur chaar takbeerein kahin. aapney Namaz mein tawaalat ki, na jaldi. phir baithney lagey to logon ne kaha : aey Abu-Hamza ! (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat hai) ye eik Ansari khatoon (ka janaza) hai aur wo isey qarib laye aur maiyat ke ooper sabz (hara) rang ka parda tha. (taboot-numaa rukawat jo aurat ki laash par rakhi jati hai) to aap uski kamar ke muqabil khadey huey aur janaza padhaya jaisey ke mard ka padhaya tha phir aap baith gaey. to Ala bin Ziyad ne puchha : aey Abu-Hamza ! kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi aisey hi janaza padhaya kartey they jaisey ke aapney padhaya hai ke chaar takbeeren kehtey aur mard ke liye uskey sar ke samney aur aurat ke liye uski kamar ke muqabil khadey hua kartey they? unhoney kaha : haan . phir usney puchha : aey Abu-Hamza ! kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad mein bhi shareek rahey hain? unhoney kaha : haan . main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ghazwae Hunain mein shareek tha ke mushrekin nikley aur ham par hamla kar diya yahan tak ke ham ne apney ghodon ko apni peethon ke peechhey dekha (ham paspa ho gaey) aur un mushrekin main eik aadmi tha jo hamein kuchley ja raha tha aur usney hamein tod ke rakh diya tha. bil-aakhir Allah taala ne unhen paspa kar diya. aur phir un logon ko laya gaya aur wo Islam par baiat karney lagey . aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se eik aadmi ne kaha tha : mujh par ye nazar hai ke agar Allah us aadmi ko ley aaya jo aaj hamein kuchaltaa raha hai to main bil-zaroor uski gardan udaaoon ga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ye sun kar) khamosh rahey aur us aadmi ko ley aaya gaya. jab usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main Allah ki taraf tauba karta hun. aur phir aap rukey rahey aur us se baiat nahin li taake wo sahabi apni nazar puri kar ley. raawi kehta hai : aur wo sahabi bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney aata raha taake aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey us shakhs ko qatl kar deney ka hukm irshad farmaeyn. jabke wo apney taur par usko qatl kar deney mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se heybiyat mein tha. isliye jab aapney dekha ke wo sahabi kuchh nahin kar raha hai to aapney us se baiat ley li . phir us sahabi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! meri nazar (ka kya hoga)? aapney farmaya : ''main to isi liye rukaa raha ke to apni nazar puri kar ley.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney mujhey aankh se ishara kyon na kar diya? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi Nabi ko layaq nahin ke aankh se ishara karey. Abu Ghalib kehtey hain : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke is amal ke mutalliq puchha jo wo aurat ki kamar ke muqabil khadey huey they. to logon ne kaha ke (pehley) ye isliye hota tha ke maiyat par taboot nahin rakha jata tha to Imam aurat ki kamar ke muqabil khada ho jata tha taake uskey liye qom se parda bin jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman ke ''mujhey logon ke sath qitaal kerney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo ( [ La-ilaah-illallah ] ( keh den.'' is hadees ki roshni mein mansookh hai jis mein ke qatl ki nazar puri kar deney ka bayan aaya hai. halanke us shakhs ne keh diya tha ke ''main tauba karta hun.''"
3195,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki iqtidaa main eik aurat ka janaza padha jo ke ayyaame nifaas (ke dinon) mein faut hui thi. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey darmiyan ke muqabil khadey huey they."
3196,"Janab Sha'bi (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik taza bani hui qabr ke paas se guzrey, to Sahaba ne us par saf banai (janaza padha gaya) aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us par chaar takbeerein kahin. Abu-Is'haq kehtey hain : maine Sha'bi (Rahimahullah) se puchha ke aap ko ye kis ne bayan kyia hai? to unhoney kaha ke eik bharosemand (qabile-aitimad) shakhsiyat ne jo us janaazey mein hazir thi yani Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma)."
3197,Abdur-Rehman bin Abi-Laila kehtey hain ke Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey janaazon par chaar takbeeren kaha kartey they. eik janaazey par aapney paanch takbeeren kahin to maine un se puchha to unhoney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye (paanch takbeeren bhi) kaha kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke mujhey Muhammad bin Musanna ki hadees khoob yaad hai.
3198,Hazrat Talha bin Abdullah bin Auf bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath eik janaza padha to unhoney sura Fatiha ki qirat ki aur kaha : ye sunnat hai.
3199,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''jab tum kisi maiyat ka janaza padho to uskey liye ikhlas se dua kiya karo.''
3200,"Hazrat Marwan bin Hakam ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya ke aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko janaza padhtey huey kaisey suna hai? Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya is sab ke bawajood jo tum ne kaha hai? usney kaha : haan . . . . raawi ne wazahat ki ke un dono ke beech is se pehley koi baat hui thi. . . . Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ye dua padha kartey they : ([اللهم ! أنت ربها وأنت خلقتها وأنت هديتها للإسلام وأنت قبضت روحها وأنت أعلم بسرها وعلانيتها جئنا شفعاء ( له ( فاغفر له]) ''aey Allah ! to is maiyat ka rab hai, to ne hi isey paida kiya hai aur deene Islam ki hidayat di hai aur to ne hi iski rooh qabz ki hai aur to iskey baatin aur zahir se ba-khoobi aagah hai, ham iskey sifarishi bin kar aaye hain to isey maaf farma dey.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Shoba ne sanad ke eik raawi Ali bin Shimaakh ke naam mein ghalati kartey huey usey Usman bin Shamaas keh diya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine Ahmed bin Ibrahim Moosli se suna jo Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se riwayat kartey they ke main jab bhi Hammad bin Zaid ki majlis mein baitha to wo Abdul-Waris aur Jaafar bin Sulaiman se riwayat leney se mana kartey they."
3201,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik janaazey par Namaz padhi to yun dua farmaee : (اللهم ! اغفر لحينا وميتنا ، وصغيرنا وكبيرنا ، وذكرنا وأنثانا ، وشاهدنا وغائبنا ، اللهم ! من أحييته منا فأحيه على الإيمان ، ومن توفيته منا فتوفه على الإسلام ، اللهم ! لا تحرمنا أجره ، ولا تضلنا بعده) ''aey Allah ! hamarey zindon aur marney walon ko bakhsh dey aur chhoton ko aur badon ko, mardon ko aur aurton ko , hazir, maujud logon ko aur jo maujud nahin hain unhen bhi bakhsh dey. aey Allah ! ham mein se jisey to zinda rakhey to usey emaan ke sath zinda rakh aur jisey to maut dey usey Islam par maut dey . aey Allah ! hamein is marney waley ke ajr se mehroom na rakh aur iskey baad hamen gumrah bhi na kar dena.''"
3202,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein eik musalman ki Namaze janaza padhaai. maine aap ko ye kehtey huey suna (اللهم ! إن فلان بن فلان في ذمتك ، فقه فتنة القبر) jabkey Abdur-Rehman bin Ibrahim ne yun kaha : (في ذمتك ، وحبل جوارك ، فقه من فتنة القبر ، وعذاب النار ، وأنت أهل الوفاء والحق ‘ اللهم فاغفر له وارحمه إنك أنت الغفور الرحيم) ''aey Allah ! falan bin falan terey zimmey (kifalat) mein hai aur teri ham-saayegi aur aman mein aa gaya hai. so to isey qabr ki aazmaesh aur aag ke azab se mehfooz farma dey, to apney wadey wafaa kerney wala aur haq wala hai. aey Allah ! isey bakhsh dey aur is par rehem farma, bila-shuba to bahut hi bakhshney wala aur rehem kerney wala hai.'' Abdur-Rehman ne sanad bayan kartey huey ((حدثنا) ke bajaey) (عن مروان بن جناح) kaha."
3203,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik kaley rang ki aurat ya mard masjid ki safai kiya karta tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ghayab paya aur uskey mutalliq daryaft farmaya to kaha gaya ke wo faut ho gaya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to tum ne mujhey bataya kyon nahin?'' phir farmaya : ''mujhey uski qabr batao.'' Sahaba ne uski nishaandehi ki to aapney us par Namaze-janaza padhi."
3204,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Shaah Najashi ki wafat ke roz uskey mutalliq logon ko khabar di aur phir unhen lekar eid gaah ki taraf gaey, unki safen banaeen aur) Namaze-janaza mein) chaar takbeeren kahin."
3205,"Hazrat Abu-Barda apney walid (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke ham Najashi ke mulk (habsha) mein chaley jaeyn. aur apni hadees bayan ki . Najashi ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain aur ye wohi hain jinkey mutalliq Hazrat Esa ibne Maryam Alehissalam ne khushkhabri di thi, agar main badshahi ke in halaat se dochaar na hota to main bil-zaroor aap ki khidmat mein hazir hota yahan tak ke aap ke jootey uthata."
3206,"Janab Muttalib (bin Abdullah bin Hantab (Rahimahullah) ( ne bayan kiya ke jab Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui aur unka janaza laya gaya aur dafn kiya gaya, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs se farmaya ke eik pathar lao magar wo usey utha na saka to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski taraf uthey. apni kalaaiyon se kapda hataayaa . . . . (hadees ke raawi) Kaseer ne kaha ke Muttalib kehtey hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kerney waley ne bataya : goya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baazuon ki safedi dekh raha hun jab aapney un se kapda hataayaa tha. . . . phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey uthaya aur qabr par sar ki taraf rakh diya aur farmaya : ''main is se apney bhai ki qabr pehchan sakoon ga aur merey ehle mein se jo koi faut hua mein usey iskey qarib dafn karunga.''"
3207,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maiyat ki haddi todnaa aisey hi hai jaisey ke zinda ki todnaa.''"
3208,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''lahad hamarey liye hai aur shaqq (shigaf) doosron ke liye hai.''"
3209,"Janab Aamir Sha'bi (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Ali, Fazal aur Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghusl diya aur unhoney hi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qabr mein utaara. Sha'bi ne kaha ke mujhey Marhab . . . . ya ibne-Abi Marhab (Suwaid bin Qais . . . .) ne bayan kiya ke unhoney apney sath Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi shamil kiya tha aur jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farigh huey to kaha : tadfeen waghaira ke amal mein aadmi ke apney ehle ke afrad hi hissey len."
3210,Hazrat Abu-Marhab se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr mein utrey they. (Abu-Marhab) kehtey hain : goya main un chaaron ko dekh raha hun.
3211,"Janab Abu-Is'haq (Sabeei (Rahimahullah) ( se riwayat hai ke Haris Aa'war ne wasiyat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazid (Hutami (Raziallahu anhu)) unki Namaze janaza padhaen . chunanche unhoney janaza padhaya , phir unhen qabr ki paainti ki taraf se qabr mein utaara aur farmaya : ye sunnat hai."
3212,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik Ansari ke janaazey mein gaey, ham qabr ke paas pahunchey to abhi tak lahad nahin bani thi. isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibla rukh ho kar baith gaey aur ham bhi aap ke sath baith gaey."
3213,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab maiyat ko qabr mein utaartey, to yun farmaya kartey : (بسم الله وعلى سنة رسول الله ) ''Allah ke naam se aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tareeqey par.'' aur ye lafz Muslim bin Ibrahim ke hain."
3214,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar di ke aap ka boodha gumrah chacha mar gaya hai. aapney farmaya : '' jao aur apney walid ko zameen mein daba aao , phir koi kaam na karna yahan tak ke merey paas aa jana.'' chunanche main gaya aur usey zameen mein daba aaya aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya aapney mujhey hukm diya to maine ghusl kiya aur aapney merey liye dua farmaee."
3215,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke uhud ke roz Ansari log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha : ham zakhmi hain aur thakey huey bhi , to aap kya irshad farmatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''qabren khodo aur khuli-khuli banao aur do-do aur teen-teen ko eik-eik qabr mein dafna do.'' kaha gaya ke aagey kisey kiya jaey? farmaya : ''jisey Quran ziyada yaad ho. Hisham kehtey hain ke merey walid Aamir bhi isi din Shahid ho gaey they aur wo do aadmiyon ke sath dafn huey they ya kaha ke eik aadmi ke sath."
3216,Humaid bin Hilal ne apni mazkura baala sanad se uskey ham-maani bayan kiya aur is mein izafa hai : ''(qabren) gahri banao.''
3217,Humaid bin Hilal ne Saad bin Hisham bin Aamir se yehi hadees riwayat ki.
3218,"Hazrat Abu-Biyaaj Asadi se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bheja aur farmaya : main tumhen us kaam par bhej raha hun jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bheja tha ke kisi oonchi qabr ko na chhodun magar usey barabar kar dun aur na kisi moorti ko magar usey mita dalun."
3219,"Abu-Ali Hamdaani ne bayan kiya ke ham Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein Roam ki sar zameen mein jazeera roads mein they ke hamara eik sathi wafat pa gaya. Hazrat Fazaala ne unki qabr ke mutalliq kaha ke isey barabar kar diya jaey, phir farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke aap qabr ko barabar kerney ka hukm detey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke roads eik samandari jazeerey ka naam hai."
3220,"Janab Qasim (Rahimahullah) (ibne Muhammad bin Abi Bakr Siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu)) kehtey hain ke main Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya ke ammaan jaan ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke do sathiyon ki qabren dikhaeyn, to unhoney meri khatir parda eik taraf kiya. teen qabren thin jo na to oonchi thin aur na zameen ke sath barabar , balke qadrey oonchi thin aur surkh maidan ki kankariyaan un par dali gaee thin. Janab Abu-Ali Loo'loo (raawi Sunan abi Abu-Dawud ( se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr aagey hai aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unke sar ke paas hain aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke paon ke paas yani Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka sar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qadmon mein hai."
3221,Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab maiyat ko dafn karkey farigh ho jatey to qabr par rukte aur farmatey : ''apney bhai ke liye istighfar karo aur Sabit qadmi ki dua karo beshak ab is se sawal kiya jaeyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne (sanad ke eik raawi Abdullah ke walid ka naam) Baheer bin Resan bayan kiya.
3222,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein aqar (janwaron ko qabr par zibeh karna) nahin hai. Imam Abdur-Razzaaq (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke logon ka mamool tha ke wo qabr ke paas gaey ya bakri waghaira zibeh kiya kartey they."
3223,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik din tashrif ley gaey aur ehale-uhud par Namaz padhi jaisey ke maiyat par padhtey hain, phir wapis tashrif ley aaye."
3224,"Janab Yazid bin Abi Habib ne ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha : beshak Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shohdaaey uhud par aath saal ke baad Namaze janaza padhi, goya ke aap zindon aur mardon ko Al-Wadaa keh rahey they."
3225,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap mana farmatey they ke qabr par baitha jaey ya isey choonaa gach (pakka) kiya jaey aur is par koi taameer ki jaey."
3226,Hazrat Sulaiman bin Musa aur Abu-Zubair (Rahimahullah) ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees bayan ki . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Usman bin Abi Sheba ne kaha : ''usko ziyada karna mana hai (usey ooncha kar diya jaey).''  aur Sulaiman bin Musa ne mazeed kaha : ''us par katba lagana mana hai.'' magar Musaddad ne apni riwayat mein (أو يزاد عليه) ka lafz zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Musaddad ki riwayat mein merey liye lafz (وأن) wazeh nahin hua tha.
3227,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala yahudiyon ko halak karey unhoney apney anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya.''
3228,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi dahakte koyley par baith jaey, wo uskey kapdey jala dey aur phir uska asar uskey jism tak pahunch jaey, ye iskey liye behtar hai us se ke kisi qabr par baithey.''"
3229,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : maine Hazrat Abu-Marsad ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, wo bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qabron par mat baitho aur na unki taraf rukh karkey Namaz padho.''"
3230,"Hazrat Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghulam they, ayyaame jahiliyat (ke dinon) mein unka naam Zahm bin Maabad tha. ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf hijrat kar aaye they. aapney puchha : ''tumhara naam kya hai? ''kaha : Zahm. aapney farmaya : ''(nahin) balke tum Bashir ho.'' ye bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chal raha tha ke aap mushrikon ki qabron ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''beshak ye log bahut badi khair se pehley hi guzar gaey (Islam laney se mehroom rahey).'' aapney ye baat teen baar farmaee , phir aap musalmanon ki qabron ke paas se guzrey , to farmaya : ''bila-shuba in logon ne bahut badi khair pa li (Islam qabool kar liya).'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nazar padi to dekha ke eik aadmi jootey pehney huey qabron par chala aa raha hai. aapney farmaya : ''aey jooton waley ! afsos hai tum par , apney jootey utaar do.'' us aadmi ne dekha, jab pehchaana ke ye Allah ke Rasool hain to usney apney jootey utaar kar phenk diye."
3231,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bandey ko jab uski qabr mein rakh diya jata hai aur uskey sathi uskey paas se janey lagtey hain, to bila-shuba wo unke jooton ki chaap sunta hai.''"
3232,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke merey walid eik doosrey aadmi ke sath dafn kiye gaey to is wajeh se merey ji mein tha ke unko wahan se nikal lun . chunanche maine unhen chhe maah baad wahan se nikala , to un mein koi tabdeeli na aai thi siwaye dadhi ke chand baalon ke jo zameen ke sath lagey huey they."
3233,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke log eik janaza lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzrey aur unhoney usko khair se yaad kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wajib ho gaee.'' phir wo eik doosra janaza lekar guzrey aur uska zikr burey andaz mein kiya to aapney farmaya : ''wajib ho gaee.'' phir aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba tum eik doosrey par gawah ho.''
3234,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni walida ki qabr par aaye to ro padey aur aap ke ird-gird sathi bhi ro diye . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine apney Rab taala se ijazat chahi ke iskey liye bakhshish ki dua karun magar mujhey ijazat nahin di gaee. phir maine ijazat chahi ke uski qabr ki ziyaarat kar lun to mujhey ijazat de-di gaee . chunanche tum bhi qabron ki ziyaarat kiya karo, bila-shuba is se maut yaad aati hai.''"
3235,"Hazrat (Sulaiman) ibne Barida apney walid (Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu)) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat se roka tha, chunanche ab unki ziyaarat kya karo . bila-shuba inki ziyaarat mein (maut ki) yaad dahani hai.''"
3236,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisi aurton par lanat farmaee hai jo qabron par jati hain aur (un logon par bhi) jo log unhen sajda gaah banatey hain ya wahan chiragh jalaatey hain.
3237,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabristaan ki taraf tashrif ley gaey to ye dua padhi (السلام عليكم دار قوم مؤمنين ، وإنا إن شاء الله بكم لاحقون) ''salamti ho tum par aey in gharon ke momin logo ! aur ham bhi Insha-Allah tumharey sath milney waley hain.''
3238,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aisey aadmi ko laya gaya jisey uski sawari ne gira kar uski gardan tod di aur wo faut ho gaya jabkey wo haalate-ehram mein tha. to aapney farmaya : ''isey uskey un do kapdon mein kafan do, beri ke pattey miley pani ke sath ghusl do aur iska sar mat dhaanpo . bila-shuba qiyamat ke roz Allah taala isey uthaeyga to ye talbiya padh raha hoga . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna, wo farmatey they ke is hadees mein paanch ehkam hain. (1) aisi maiyat ko do hi kapdon mein kafan diya jaey. (2) tamam ghuslon mein beri ke pattey istimal kiye jaeyn. (3) uska sar na dhanpa jaey. (4) aur na khushbu hi lagai jaey. (5) aur kafan uskey apney maal mein se liya jaey."
3239,Hazrat Saeed bin Jubair (Rahimahullah) Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se is hadees ki manind riwayat kartey hain. kaha : ''aur usko do kapdon mein kafan do. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Sulaiman bin Harab ki Ayub se riwayat mein lafz yun hain : (sobiya) ''yani uskey apney do kapdon mein kafan do.'' jabke Amr ki riwayat mein (saubain) aaya hai. ''do kapdon mein kafan do.'' (uskey apney hon ya kisi doosrey ne diye hon.) ibne Ubaid ki riwayat jo Ayub se hai us mein (fee saubain) ka lafz hai. jabkey Amr ne (saubiya) kaha hai. aur sirf Sulaiman ne ye izafa kya : ''usey Hanoot (khushbu) bhi na lagao.''
3240,"Ayub, Saeed bin Jubair se aur wo Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se Sulaiman ki riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kartey hain, yani ''(fee saubain)'' do kapdon mein kafan do.''"
3241,"Janab Saeed bin Jubair (Rahimahullah) , Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik mohrim aadmi ko uski sawari ne gira diya aur uski gardan tod di aur is se wo faut ho gaya , usko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya to aapney farmaya : ''isey ghusl do, kafan pehnao lekin sar na dhaanpo aur na khushbu hi lagao , bila-shuba ye talbiya pukartey huey uthaya jaeyga.''"
